<servinfosub id = "AENBP70AA504022003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Confirm that ignition is OFF.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ACC.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Repeat Step 1) through 3) several times.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70AA504022004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
This DTC might be detected when battery is run down or the voltage is very low.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Before performing troubleshooting, remove aftermarket devices connected to the line via “ACC” fuse and devices that have a backup power supply function located in their accessory socket (non-genuine devices, optional parts, audio, etc.). Voltage from these devices may cause this DTC to be detected during diagnosis.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENBP70AA504022005">
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022006">
<title>
Parameter check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Connect SUZUKI scan tool to DLC when ignition is OFF.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check “Accessory Relay” and “Accessory Switch” displayed on SUZUKI scan tool. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA504007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
End. (Intermittent trouble.)
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022007">
<title>
ACC relay power supply circuit (switch side) check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Confirm that ignition is OFF.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Remove ACC relay.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check that voltage between “A1” circuit and ground is battery voltage.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness and “IGN” fuse.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022008">
<title>
Fuse check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check “ACC” fuse.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 5.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022009">
<title>
ACC relay signal circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition OFF.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect “L10” connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “L10” connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “B1” circuit and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “B1” circuit terminal and each terminal at ACC relay connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace “ACC” fuse and keyless start control module and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness, and then replace “ACC” fuse.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022010">
<title>
ACC relay signal circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition OFF.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect “L10” connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “L10” connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “B1” circuit: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “B1” circuit terminal and each terminal at ACC relay connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “B1” circuit: approx. 0 V (with ignition ON)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 6.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022011">
<title>
ACC relay power supply circuit (coil side) check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “C1” circuit: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “C1” circuit and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “C1” circuit terminal and each terminal at ACC relay connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “C1” circuit: approx. 0 V (with ignition ON)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 7.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022012">
<title>
ACC relay check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check ACC relay. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA206006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 8.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace ACC relay.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504022013">
<title>
DTC check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition OFF.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Connect “L10” connector and install ACC relay.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform DTC confirmation procedure.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA504003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is current DTC B1191 detected?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace keyless start control module and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
End. (Intermittent trouble.)
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
